object.script:
i=property.getNumber R=i("R") G=i("G") B=i("B") R2=i("R2") G2=i("G2") B2=i("B2") mrps1=i("max rps") sdr=screen.drawRect sdrf=screen.drawRectF ssc=screen.setColor sdl=screen.drawLine sdt=screen.drawText ign=input.getNumber igb=input.getBool osn=output.setNumber osb=output.setBool gear=0 st=false prg=0 mas={"-","r","n","1","2","3","4","5","6","7","-"} function onTick()
gear=ign(1) power=igb(32) if power and not st then prg=prg+1 else prg=0 end if prg>30 then prg=30 end if prg>29 then st=true elseif not power then st=false end selectr=ign(29) rps1=ign(30) speed=ign(31) range=ign(32) if (rps1>(mrps1-1)) then cr=255;cg=0;cb=0 else cr=R;cg=G;cb=B end end function onDraw() ssc(0,0,0) sdrf(0,0,64,64) if power and not st then ssc(R,G,B) sdt(11,9,"K".."T") sdl(11,15,(prg/3.5)+11,15) end if st then ssc(R2,G2,B2) sdrf(0,4,32,7) sdrf(0,22,32,7) sdrf(0,13,32,7) ssc(R,G,B) --screen.drawText(1,4,"kmph") screen.drawTextBox(9,4,15,5,math.floor(speed*3.6),-0.5,0) --screen.drawText(7,22,"rkm") screen.drawTextBox(16,22,15,5,math.floor(range),-0.5,0) --sdr(0,11,31,8) ssc(cr,cg,cb) sdt(14,13,mas[selectr+3]) ssc(55,55,55) sdt(8,13,mas[selectr+2]) sdt(20,13,mas[selectr+4]) end end

object.script:
ign=input.getNumber igb=input.getBool osn=output.setNumber osb=output.setBool a=0 w=0 br=0 function onTick() wsp=ign(5) wsm=ign(6) adp=ign(7) adm=ign(8) invert=igb(1) wl=ign(9) ws=ign(4) ad=ign(3)
if ws>0 then w=(w+wsp) end if ws<0 then w=(w-wsp) end if ws==0 and w>0 then w=(w-wsm) end if ws==0 and w<0 then w=(w+wsm) end if threshold(w,-0.05,0.05) and ws==0 then w=0 end w=clamp(w,1,-1) if ad>0 then a=(a+adp) end if ad<0 then a=(a-adp) end if ad==0 and a>0 then a=(a-adm) end if ad==0 and a<0 then a=(a+adm) end if threshold(a,-0.05,0.05) and ad==0 then a=0 end a=clamp(a,1,-1) wss=w+ign(2) add=a+ign(1) if invert then leftwheel=-add*wl;rightwheel=add*wl else leftwheel=add*wl;rightwheel=-add*wl end osn(1,add) osn(2,wss) osn(3,leftwheel) osn(4,rightwheel) end --clamp(number,max,min) function clamp(x,p,m) if x>p then x=p end if x<m then x=m end return x end --threshold(number,low,high) function threshold(x,y,z) if x>y and x<z then return true else return false end end

ign=input.getNumber igb=input.getBool osn=output.setNumber osb=output.setBool gear=0 abs=math.abs
function onTick() ws=ign(2) up=igb(1) and not up1 up1=igb(1) down=igb(2) and not down1 down1=igb(2)
if up then gear=gear+1 end if down then gear=gear-1 end if gear<-1 then gear=-1 end if gear>7 then gear=7 end
agear=abs(gear) if gear<0 then r=true else r=false end if agear==0 then clutch=0 else clutch=ws*100 end if agear==1 then b1=true;b2=true;b3=true end if agear==2 then b1=true;b2=true;b3=false end if agear==3 then b1=true;b2=false;b3=true end if agear==4 then b1=true;b2=false;b3=false end if agear==5 then b1=false;b2=true;b3=true end if agear==6 then b1=false;b2=true;b3=false end if agear==7 then b1=false;b2=false;b3=true end
osb(1,b1) osb(2,b2) osb(3,b3) osb(6,r) osn(1,gear) osn(2,clutch) end
